e":119.302938,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3501","Title":"福州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"890c1dbbe77d4117911a09699bb90824\");'><span id='890c1dbbe77d4117911a09699bb90824_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年</a>，70岁</div><div id='890c1dbbe77d4117911a09699bb90824' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年10月15日</a>，游武夷而归。福唐守敷文阁学士汪应辰以书礼来迎，求质所疑。十月，公应聘至福唐，方三日，卒于府治之馆舍。其孙护丧以归。门人朱紫阳为状，福守汪应辰墓志。至理宗淳祐六年，提刑杨栋为请谥于朝。七年，赐谥文靖。去先生殁时二十有五年矣。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"李侗 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1093-1163)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：毛念恃《延平李先生年谱》、陈利华《朱熹和李侗在南平九峰山的行踪考辩》　录入整理：彭洁明</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 8, 118.400943, 27.201048, 9)\">0-70岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">南平</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">建瓯</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">南平</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">建瓯</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">铅山</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">邵武</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">南平</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">福州</a></p>"}]}